          "source": "pattern:empty-and-system-states",
          "content": [
            {
              "prose": "System states communicate the current condition of the platform or a specific view. Clear, direct copy helps users understand what happened and what to do next."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "Empty state",
          "source": "pattern:empty-and-system-states",
          "content": [
            {
              "prose": "Empty states appear when users have not yet created items, or when filters return no results. Clear copy and a direct CTA reduce friction and encourage engagement."
            }
          ],
          "subsections": [
            {
              "subheading": "When to use",
              "content": [
                {
                  "bullets": [
                    "When users have not yet created or uploaded items.",
                    "When [filters](/components/form-input-selection/search-filters/) result in no visible results.",
                    "To encourage engagement with a clear next action."
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "subheading": "Style",
              "content": [
                {
                  "bullets": [
                    "Use a short, instructive headline (noun phrase or imperative verb).",
                    "Follow with one concise sentence that explains what the user can do.",
                    "Provide one primary action (for example, **Create dataset**).",
                    "Do not use `No results found` as a standalone message without guidance."
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "subheading": "Do / Don't",
              "content": [
                {
                  "do": "No items found / Add your first dataset to start exploring.",
                  "dont": "No results."
                },
                {
                  "do": "Nothing here yet / Create a connection to get started.",
                  "dont": "There are no items to display at this time."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "subheading": "Example",
              "content": [
                {
                  "table": {
                    "headers": [
                      "Element",
                      "Example text"
                    ],
                    "rows": [
                      [
                        "Title",
                        "No items found"
                      ],
                      [
                        "Body",
                        "Add your first dataset to start exploring."
                      ],
                      [
                        "CTA",
                        "Create dataset"
                      ]
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "Error state",
          "source": "pattern:empty-and-system-states",
          "content": [
            {
              "prose": "Error states communicate that something failed or a resource could not be loaded. Copy must be specific, non-blaming, and actionable."
            }
          ],
          "subsections": [
            {
              "subheading": "When to use",
              "content": [
                {
                  "bullets": [
                    "When something fails or a resource cannot be loaded.",
                    "When a user action fails to complete."
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "subheading": "Style",
              "content": [
                {
                  "bullets": [
                    "Be specific about what went wrong where possible.",
                    "Offer a resolution step or next action.",
                    "Do not use technical error codes as the primary message.",
                    "Do not blame the user."
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "subheading": "Example",
              "content": [
                {
                  "table": {
                    "headers": [
                      "Element",
                      "Example text"
                    ],
                    "rows": [
                      [
                        "Title",
                        "Something went wrong"
                      ],
                      [
                        "Body",
                        "There was an error creating your item. Try again or contact support if the problem continues."
                      ],
                      [
                        "Primary CTA",
                        "Try again"
                      ]
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "Maintenance state",
          "source": "pattern:empty-and-system-states",
          "content": [
            {
              "prose": "Maintenance states inform users that part of the platform is temporarily unavailable due to planned or unplanned work."
            }
          ],
          "subsections": [
            {
              "subheading": "Style",
              "content": [
                {
                  "bullets": [
                    "Explain what is affected and for how long.",
                    "Provide an estimated time to resolution when available.",
                    "Include a single action if there is something the user can do (for example, **Refresh**)."
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "subheading": "Example",
              "content": [
                {
                  "table": {
                    "headers": [
                      "Element",
                      "Example text"
                    ],
                    "rows": [
                      [
                        "Title",
                        "Scheduled maintenance in progress"
                      ],
                      [
                        "Body",
                        "Reports may be unavailable until 12:00 PM EST."
                      ],
                      [
                        "CTA",
                        "Refresh"
                      ]
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "Success state",
          "source": "pattern:empty-and-system-states",
          "content": [
            {
              "prose": "Success states confirm that a user action completed. They often follow an action that previously triggered an empty state."
            }
          ],
          "subsections": [
            {
              "subheading": "Style",
              "content": [
                {
                  "bullets": [
                    "Confirm what was completed, not just that it succeeded.",
                    "Keep copy brief. One line is usually sufficient.",
                    "Offer a logical next action."
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
